'''X11'''是一种算法，现在主要用于[[达世币]]之[[工作量证明]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://docs.dash.org/zh_CN/latest/introduction/features.html#x11-hash-algorithm |title=X11算法 |publisher=Dash Core Group |accessdate=2018-11-15 |archive-date=2020-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413220444/https://docs.dash.org/zh_CN/latest/introduction/features.html#x11-hash-algorithm }}</ref>。X11把11种[[密碼雜湊函數]]串联，按顺序把上一函数之哈希值传递至下一个函数，最后得出一个哈希结果。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://github.com/dashpay/dash/wiki/Whitepaper|title=dashpay/dash|website=GitHub|access-date=2018-11-14|archive-date=2022-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220411140931/https://github.com/dashpay/dash/wiki/Whitepaper}}</ref>

X11包括以下11个函数<ref>{{cite web|url=https://wk588.com/2874-1-1.html|title=X11达世币矿机是如何坑苦矿工的 收益为何会爆降-专业矿机挖矿-挖矿网|website=wk588.com|access-date=2019-05-15|archive-date=2020-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413220455/https://wk588.com/2874-1-1.html}}</ref>，全部皆为{{link-en|NIST散列函数竞赛|NIST hash function competition}}之参赛者<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mycryptopedia.com/x11-algorithm-explained/|title=X11 Algorithm Explained - Mycryptopedia|date=2018-08-05|publisher=|access-date=2018-11-14|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109033030/https://www.mycryptopedia.com/x11-algorithm-explained/}}</ref><ref>[http://csrc.nist.gov/groups/ST/hash/sha-3/Round3/submissions_rnd3.html Third (Final) Round Candidates] {{Wayback|url=http://csrc.nist.gov/groups/ST/hash/sha-3/Round3/submissions_rnd3.html |date=20101218080251 }} Retrieved 9 Nov 2011</ref>：
# [[BLAKE]]
# Blue Midnight Wish<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.item.ntnu.no/people/personalpages/fac/danilog/blue_midnight_wish|title=blue_midnight_wish|accessdate=10 November 2008|author=Svein Johan Knapskog|author2=Danilo Gligoroski|author3=Vlastimil Klima|author4=Mohamed El-Hadedy|author5=Jørn Amundsen|author6=Stig Frode Mjølsnes|date=November 4, 2008|archive-date=2013-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112214539/http://www.item.ntnu.no/people/personalpages/fac/danilog/blue_midnight_wish}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mat.dtu.dk/people/S.Thomsen/bmw/bmw-pseudo.pdf|title=Pseudo-cryptanalysis of Blue Midnight Wish|format=PDF|author=Søren S. Thomsen|year=2009|accessdate=19 May 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090902193808/http://www2.mat.dtu.dk/people/S.Thomsen/bmw/bmw-pseudo.pdf|archivedate=2009-09-02|df=}}</ref>
# [[Grøstl]]
# {{le|JH (散列函数)|JH (hash function)|JH}}
# [[SHA-3|Keccak]]
# {{le|Skein (散列函数)|Skein (hash function)|Skein}}
# Luffa<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ehash.iaik.tugraz.at/uploads/e/ea/Luffa_Specification.pdf|title=Hash Function Luffa: Specification|format=PDF|author=Dai Watanabe|author2=Christophe De Canniere|author3=Hisayoshi Sato|date=31 October 2008|accessdate=11 December 2008|archive-date=2013-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112215454/http://ehash.iaik.tugraz.at/uploads/e/ea/Luffa_Specification.pdf}}</ref>
# {{le|CubeHash}}
# SHAvite-3<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ehash.iaik.tugraz.at/uploads/f/f5/Shavite.pdf|title=The SHAvite-3 Hash Function|format=PDF|author=Eli Biham|author2=Orr Dunkelman|accessdate=11 December 2008|archive-date=2013-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112212134/http://ehash.iaik.tugraz.at/uploads/f/f5/Shavite.pdf}}</ref>
# {{le|SIMD (散列函数)|SIMD (hash function)|SIMD}}
# ECHO<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ehash.iaik.tugraz.at/uploads/9/91/Echo.pdf|title=SHA-3 Proposal: ECHO|format=PDF|author=Henri Gilbert|author2=Ryad Benadjila|author3=Olivier Billet|author4=Gilles Macario-Rat|author5=Thomas Peyrin|author6=Matt Robshaw|author7=Yannick Seurin|date=October 29, 2008|accessdate=11 December 2008|archive-date=2013-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112212107/http://ehash.iaik.tugraz.at/uploads/9/91/Echo.pdf}}</ref>

X11算法縱使包含大量函數，內存消耗量較大<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.jcr.cacrnet.org.cn:8080/mmxb/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=275|title=区块链安全研究综述|author=斯雪明,徐蜜雪,苑超|date=2018-09-28|journal=|access-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515081637/http://www.jcr.cacrnet.org.cn:8080/mmxb/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do%3FattachType%3DPDF%26id%3D275|archive-date=2019-05-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但效率比起不少散列算法皆高。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mifengcha.com/wenda/230417|title=什么是X11算法-蜜蜂查|website=mifengcha.com|access-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515040948/https://mifengcha.com/wenda/230417|archive-date=2019-05-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

